On-time vaccination throughout childhood is essential because it helps provide immunity before children are exposed to potentially life-threatening diseases. Vaccines are tested to ensure that they are safe and effective for children to receive at the recommended ages. As communities open up, it’s important your child goes in for their well-child visit. Why Vaccinate More details Making the Vaccine Decision Learn all about vaccines and immunity, what vaccines are made of, and how they are kept safe.
